Air Officer Commanding, Logistics Command, Lagos, Air Vice Marshal (AVM) Lawal Shittu Alao, has been awarded the Fellowship of the Association of Industrial Security and Safety Operations of Nigeria (AISSON) in recognition of his leading role in promoting security, safety culture and consciousness in Nigeria.
